  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Let's teach PM Ranil a lesson soon - Sajith reacts in the House",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister invites us to come and teach us a lesson. But due to the people teaching him a lesson, he is currently sitting in the parliament alone on the national list.",
        "Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa said that I will soon teach the Prime Minister a lesson on receiving foreign aid.",
        "He said this in his speech in response to the Prime Minister's special speech on Tuesday 05th in the Parliament. As he continued there,",
        "The Prime Minister informed the House about the declining economy. But let's get it today. Diesel. The Prime Minister did not offer any solution to the problems of the people on the gas line.",
        "That is what people have been waiting for. Farmers do not have enough fertilizer. Triposha is closed. There is no solution to this problem in the Prime Minister's speech.",
        "Similarly, a cabinet minister has demanded ransom from a company in Japan. We ask whether the government, which has collapsed due to such corruption and fraud, can build the country.",
        "Similarly, I myself went to the opening ceremony of the Qatar Aid Agency in our last government.",
        "But the government said the money from the Qatar Charity Fund was funding terrorism. Now they are going to Qatar for fuel. We are ashamed.",
        "The government is fueling sectarianism and antagonizing the entire Middle East. There are only two influential people in Middle Eastern countries, one is Ranasinghe Premadasa and the other is Mahinda Rajapaksh.",
        "Mahinda Rajapaksh has lost that honor by fueling communalism. After the arrival of Gotabaya Rajapaksh, he increased it further. Currently, the Qatar Fund has ruled that there is no problem.",
        "Also the Prime Minister invites us to come and teach us a lesson. But the people taught him a lesson and now he is sitting alone in the parliament on the national list. He said that he will abolish the age of queue after coming to office.",
        "He said that he will bring dollars to the country. But today the entire country has been recognized as the Prime Minister who can't do anything. I will inform the Prime Minister that I will soon teach the lesson of receiving foreign aid. Similarly, I also inform the Prime Minister that the United People's Power has the support of the Middle East countries. said."
      ],
